The Resulting effects last until your next turn. 1: Opposing characters modify defense +1. 2: All characters can use Phasing/Teleport. 3: Each player chooses a character and the chosen characters modify all combat values +1. 4: Generate 4 blocking terrain markers each within range and line of fire. At the beginning of your next turn remove them. 5: Friendly characters modify attack +1. 6: Friendly characters modify all combat values +1.

special_powers.name: IN THE MINDS OF MORTALS
special_powers.description: Shape Change, Stealth. Once per turn, when a character of less points within line of fire makes an attack, you may reroll one die of that attack.

special_powers.name: TERRIGENESIS TWICE
special_powers.description: When a friendly character targets Gorgon with Perplex, after resolutions roll a D6. If the result is less than Gorgon's click number, modify the chosen value by an additional +1

special_powers.name: BUTTING HEADS
special_powers.description: Modify defense +2 when attacked by a character using Charge or Hypersonic Speed.

special_powers.name: BULLHEADED
special_powers.description: Charge. When Gorgon uses it, you may choose to not halve his speed value. If you do, he can only move in a direct path.

special_powers.name: TRAMPLE AND GORE
special_powers.description: Quake. When Gorgon uses it and hit more than one character, choose a hit character and roll a d6. Increase the damage dealt to that character by half the result.

special_powers.name: TERRIGENESIS TWICE
special_powers.description: When a friendly character targets Medusa with Perplex, after resolutions roll a D6. If the result is less than Medusa's click number, modify the chosen value by an additional +1

special_powers.name: LETHAL LOCKS
special_powers.description: Plasticity, Giant Reach: 3. Telekinesis as FREE, but replace all "6" with "3" in the text of the power.

special_powers.name: LOCKJAW'S TUNING FORK
special_powers.description: FREE: Improved Movement: Ignores Characters, Ignores Elevated Terrain, Ignores Hindering Terrain, Ignores Blocking Terrain. Passenger: 2, but only to carry characters that share a keyword regardless of ::Wing Symbol::. Move up to 3 squares.

special_powers.name: ALIEN SYMBIOTE
special_powers.description: Plasticity, Shape Change. Venom Black Panther automatically breaks away.

special_powers.name: CALL IN HELP FROM THE VENOMVERSE!
special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Venom Black Panther hits an opposing character, after resolutions you may roll a d6. 3-6: Place another friendly character whose name includes "Venom" adjacent to Venom Black Panther.

special_powers.name: AT HOME IN THE SHADOWS
special_powers.description: Stealth

special_powers.name: I WILL USE THIS WEAPON ANY WAY I CAN TO DEFEND MY HOME
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs, Poison, Quake, Steal Energy.

special_powers.name: CALL IN HELP FROM THE VENOMVERSE!
special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Captain Venom hits an opposing character, after resolutions you may roll a d6. 3-6: Place another friendly character whose name includes "Venom" adjacent to Captain Venom.

special_powers.name: EDDIE, YOU'RE JUST THE MAN WE NEED
special_powers.description: If Captain Venom is on a Monster themed team, your maximum number of Themed Team Probability Control uses this game is 6 (instead of 3).

special_powers.name: READY TO SERVE MY SPECIES
special_powers.description: Leadership. When another friendly character with the Monster keyword attacks, modify its attack +1 if Captain Venom attacked this turn.

special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Venom Gwenpool hits an opposing character, after resolutions you may roll a d6. 3-6: Place another friendly character whose name includes "Venom" adjacent to Venom Gwenpool.

special_powers.name: LETHAL PROTECTOR...ESS. PROTECTRESS? WE'RE WORKING ON IT
special_powers.description: Energy Shield/Deflection, Super Senses. If Venom Gwenpool hasn't failed a Shape Change roll this turn, adjacent friendly characters can use Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: THIS ISN'T CANON, WE CAN KILL ANYONE!
special_powers.description: Exploit Weakness. At the beginning of your turn, you may deal 1 penetrating damage to an adjacent opposing character -or- 1 unavoidable damage to an adjacent friendly character. If you do either, heal Venom Gwenpool 1 click.

special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Venom Iron Man hits an opposing character, after resolutions you may roll a d6. 3-6: Place another friendly character whose name includes "Venom" adjacent to Venom Iron Man.

special_powers.name: ARMORED ASSAULT
special_powers.description: Combat Reflexes, Super Senses, Toughness.

special_powers.name: TARGETING SLOW- MOVING FOOD
special_powers.description: When Venom Iron Man attacks, modify attack +1 if all targets have one or more action tokens. When Venom Iron Man attacks, modify damage +1 if all targets have two action tokens.

special_powers.description: Plasticity, Shape Change. Venom Rocket Raccoon automatically breaks away.

special_powers.name: CALL IN HELP FROM THE VENOMVERSE!
special_powers.description: Once per turn for all characters with this trait, when Venom Rocket Raccoon hits an opposing character, after resolutions you may roll a d6. 3-6: Place another friendly character whose name includes "Venom" adjacent to Venom Rocket Raccoon.

special_powers.name: I GOT BETTER STUFF IN MY ARSENAL
special_powers.description: When Venom Rocket Raccoon destroys one or more pieces of blocking terrain, after resolutions give him a Rummage token, maximum 3. // FREE: Remove any number of Rummage tokens and choose attack, damage or range. This turn, modify the chosen combat value +1 for each token removed.

special_powers.name: RIP AND TEAR
special_powers.description: Blades/Claws/Fangs. When Venom Spider-Man uses it and the d6 roll was 5 or 6, after resolutions move (up to speed value) and then make a close attack targeting another opposing character. (You can't use Blades/Claws/Fangs during this second attack.)

special_powers.name: INDISCRIMINATE APPETITE
special_powers.description: Battle Fury. POWER: Choose an adjacent character (friendly or opposing). If the target is friendly, deal them 1 unavoidable damage and heal Venom Spider-Man 1 click. If the target is opposing, make a close attack targeting them. If it hits, after resolutions deal them 2 penetrating damage and heal Venom Spider-Man 1 click.

special_powers.name: I NEED THREE YEARS TO FULLY RETURN
special_powers.description: Once per game when Captain Marvel would be KO'd, instead give him 3 Resurrection tokens and place him on this card.//At the beginning of your turn, if Captain Marvel is on this card, remove a Resurrection token. When the last one is removed, place Captain Marvel in any square along the edge of the map on click #3. Protected: Pulse Wave

special_powers.name: I'M COMING BACK TO SAVE EVERYONE
special_powers.description: When Captain Marvel is placed on the map by use of "I Need Three Years To Fully Return", all standard characters that were on a starting force that were KO'd this game are placed on the map on their starting click this game and given a Spirit token. Friendly characters are placed along the same edge of the map Captain Marvel is, and opposing characters on the opposite edge. Until your next turn, characters placed this way can't be attacked.//This game, characters with Spirit tokens can't be replaced, can't generate bystanders and aren't scored. This game, when a character with a Spirit token takes damage, remove it from the game immediately.

special_powers.name: SOMETIMES YOU JUST HAVE TO COMMIT
special_powers.description: Charge, Flurry. When Scarlet Spider uses Flurry and hits with both attacks, after resolutions remove all action tokens from him.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: [Wing Symbol], Toughness, Modify speed +2.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: When this character hits, if friendly to this equipment, after resolutions you may equip this object to a hit character. (It will unequip other equipment.) // If this character is friendly to this equipment it can use Super Senses but only succeeds on a 6. // If this character is opposing to this equipment it can't be given actions to equip and modifies speed -2.

special_powers.name: EFECT
special_powers.description: Incapacitate with a maximum range value of 4. When this character uses it and hits, instead of giving an action token you may have hit targets gain Immobile until your next turn. (They still take 1 penetrating damage if they had 2 action tokens.)

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Giant Reach: 2, Flurry, Improved Movement: Elevated, Hindering.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: [Wing Symbol], Running Shot. If this character is named Green Goblin or can already use Running Shot, this character can use Hypersonic Speed.

special_powers.name: EFFECT
special_powers.description: Plasticity, Shape Change. This character automatically breaks away.

special_powers.name: Rubble
special_powers.description: Characters occupying or adjacent to an orange square have 'FREE: Roll a d6. 3-4 Generate a standard light object. 5-6 Generate a standard light or heavy object.' (Place the object adjacent to that character.)

special_powers.name: Consolation
special_powers.description: When placing objects at the beginning of the game, you may generate and place 3 additional standard objects.

special_powers.name: I Keep the Trains Running
special_powers.description: Orange Lines indicate numbered tracks. Each track has the number of the die icons near its edges. At the beginning of the game, choose a friendly character. That character and the character occupying the dotted orange square have#58 'FREE: Roll a d6. You may have this Location make a close attack with 10 attack and 2 damage targeting all characters in that resulting track. 6: You may choose a Track. After resolutions, each attacked character is placed in a square adjacent to their current square that is not in that Track (active player's choice). If the character given this action is named The Skull, instead roll 2d6 and choose either as the result.'

special_powers.name: Consolation
special_powers.description: Opposing characters modify defense -1 when targeted by Mind Control, Incapacitate, or Telekinesis.
